data.description: Beautiful ranch home is on a 1.495 private acre lot. This ranch has a long extended driveway for additional privacy. The 3/2 floor plan is open with some newer features like flooring, new carpet 2023, interior paint, roof, SS appliances, security doors, just to name a few. Did I mention NO HOA, NO RENTAL Restrictions, this will be a great home for a 1st time home buyer or an investor as a rental. This home had ONLY 1 owner since construction. Set up a showing today before it's too late!
